Hiram Keller https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hiram_Keller 0 Hiram Keller (May 3, 1944 – January 20, 1997), born Hiram Keller Undercofler Jr., was an American stage and film actor who starred in European films. He is best known for his role as Ascyltus in Federico Fellini's 1969 film Satyricon.
